e":"2019-09-03T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed423836efc139fd9ed06fe4a245882319a42480","tid":1536150,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"水革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce869a7d2dcb5bf61b5ab81bb4dfc0b744a2cc15","tid":1536150,"uid":200663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"流水革命 好聽啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5370530dbe08e8b54ff284c4aa094742c6a860d9","tid":1536150,"uid":285243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce869a7d2dcb5bf61b5ab81bb4dfc0b744a2cc15","tid":1536150,"uid":200663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"流水革命 好聽啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d3613711788233ad26f90a2cba07e636fb1862","tid":1536150,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb5b1c472b3367bdffbb5661145e3d917602372","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"需要正評及幫推<br />\n協助中共增加敏感詞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"本來以為 活動 同 小姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經夠勁<br />\n宜家水都唔講得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fe67b1aecdde352e909066735c9b2230b812ef","tid":1536150,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"176119b13fa00b396c5b7c532ea6635586129e46","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"說是北宋的時候，常州有個叫田登的太守，對自己的名字特別忌諱，不允許其他人說「登」字，只要有人提到了這個字，必然惹得太守大怒，所以他身邊的吏卒很多不小心就被打板子了！<br />\n於是整個常州都把「燈」字叫成火。而到了一年一度的元宵佳節。依照以往的慣例，州城裡都要放三天焰火，點三天花燈表示慶祝。而且州府衙門要提前貼出告示，讓老百姓到時候前來觀燈。<br />\n<br />\n可是這次，卻讓出告示的官員感到左右為難。怎麼寫呢？用上「燈」字，要觸犯太守；不用「燈」字，意思又表達不明白。<br />\n想了好久，這個寫告示的官員告示上就寫成了「本州依例放火三日」。 告示貼出後，老百姓看了都驚吵喧鬧起來。尤其是一些外地來的客人，更是丈二和尚摸不著頭腦，還真的以為官府要在城裡放三天火呢！大家紛紛收拾行李，爭相離開這是非之地。當地的老百姓，平時對於田登的專制蠻橫無理已經是非常不滿，這次看了官府貼出的這張告示，更是氣憤萬分，忿忿地說：「只許州官放火，不許百姓點燈，這是什麼世道！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1qc6fdc/321r0001ss97pn0np53s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1qc6fdc%2F321r0001ss97pn0np53s.jpg&h=8a7ff9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/bqvyok9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Fbqvyok9.html&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6voVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8888d318\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/bqvyok9.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"連登"},{"pid":"cd1394a78e4b928c938c609ec2e48cb19f1e6327","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c01c4c2276c96f46c1b09c57d6291a0cc59b9de","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"據中國時報今天報道，就反逃犯條例風波中國港澳辦提三底線。<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院港澳辦發言人楊光29日表示，一國兩制是個完整概念，一國是本、是根，根生才能葉茂，有三條底線不能觸碰，一是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不允許任何危害國家主權安全行為</span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不允許挑戰中央權力</span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不允許香港對內地進行滲透破壞</span></span>，他強調這三條紅線不可觸碰。"},{"pid":"22cd5baef90c378c71415df1ca205ad1ac72389d","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c01c4c2276c96f46c1b09c57d6291a0cc59b9de","tid":1536150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"據中國時報今天報道，就反逃犯條例風波中國港澳辦提三底線。<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院港澳辦發言人楊光29日表示，一國兩制是個完整概念，一國是本、是根，根生才能葉茂，有三條底線不能觸碰，一是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不允許任何危害國家主權安全行為</span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不允許挑戰中央權力</span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不允許香港對內地進行滲透破壞</span></span>，他強調這三條紅線不可觸碰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:41:46.000Z","msg":"楊光講話沒有更多涉及官方絕不允許香港對內地進行滲透破壞的內容。"},{"pid":"ed96d554848bd2ec70d24bcf7b20c6ed327ecef6","tid":1536150,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"water"},{"pid":"75226165dd13d52458a708d1983fe119d96eb296","tid":1536150,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"#水=革命"},{"pid":"960da62329cc3381ee072b4e4a3d7ba288e88be5","tid":1536150,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"#水 #water #H20<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d7d9ac44ccfb95ffca858d415ceeb1390b8c1","tid":1536150,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b5304f7f915b4e0d33f60044ddf8cef6e790441","tid":1536150,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"礦泉x"},{"pid"